-10T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"大埔先"},{"pid":"d3d2a41926bada54ca6dc67d5bed699848150303","tid":1439023,"uid":19403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6sZRC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6sZRC2.jpg&h=e2c8213c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f0c98e0f9e3c1332c26869a24af2d0e714e0151","tid":1439023,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰 **不指揮**</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439078</a><br />\n<br />\n麥麥加推<br />\n[突發] 人人都可以做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437607</a>"},{"pid":"246c0b79b65f461dd28fbf329906204607efa344","tid":1439023,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:10:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54395e550c6b21f241aa39dc498775baa1139886","tid":1439023,"uid":62481,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"想發表少少意見 <br />\n小妹其實差唔多次次都有去<br />\n由和理非去到淺黃<br />\n罷工都做足 <br />\n不過tbh 運動開始比人一種失敗既感覺<br />\n果日罷工本應有力 <br />\n但最後做出黎就好似平時d集會遊行咁<br />\n雖然講出口話攰 係可恥<br />\n但不得不承認大家都攰<br />\n逢星期一至五要番工<br />\n星期六/日就上街<br />\n如果有成果 當然會願意做<br />\n但依加見到既係唔止無用<br />\n連啲升級死線都好無力<br />\ntbh叫人罷買 真係做到？<br />\n又或者咁講 幾多人真係會做<br />\n做完成果多唔多 易唔易見 問心就可以<br />\n<br />\n我覺得機場集會係有用既<br />\n至少呢步都幾痛下<br />\n不過人唔多 同埋其他集會個個星期都有<br />\n雖然做到遍地開花<br />\n但根本係同時消耗緊香港人<br />\n特別係和理非同埋淺黃<br />\n依加連一啲根本好恐怖既新聞<br />\n都開始變成平常<br />\n大家係咪應該停一停 去諗下點先落到一步有力既棋呢？"},{"pid":"1423ffbaf86f4b701beb010d5d0cf27e4d61cd27","tid":1439023,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a5f42f3fcc895680c6cdc162a30a0609dca6b6e4","tid":1439023,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"推行動post呀<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5524a522497f4e17898604629d06a9e342b5055","tid":1439023,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"10/8大埔遊行取消 要贏唔洗行 今日轉左場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435307</a>"}]}